Looking for Hope (score 0)

  • Sum of all region (country or state) scores
  • GREEN - Region score=0: Decrease on both new daily case and daily death
  • ORANGE - Region score=1: Region score=1: Decrease on daily case
  • RED - Region score=2: Still increasing on new daily case and death numbers

This reports covered the below cases

  • Confirmed cases - The total number is the key metrics, and its daily growth is monitored
  • Number of Death cases - Death can reflect to the status of Virus infection and medical capability
  • Recoverd case - Good news come from this number
  • Recoverd ratio - recovered/confirmed (0..1)
  • Confirmed growth (%) - The daily growth of the confirmed number (0..100)
  • Death ratio - The death ratio against the confirmed number (0..1)

How to read the report:

  • Confirmed number - confirmed cases, watch the growth number
  • Death numer - watch the ratio and trend
  • Recovered number - see the ratio compaering to comnfirmed number
  • Confirmed growth - see the trend of today's growth v.s. the history
  • Death ratio - see the growth
